# Manifests are source of truth

| Goal | Edit | Then |
|------|------|------|
| New raylib import | `raylib-exports.manifest.json` | `generate` |
| Public API method | `facades.manifest.json`, `hud.manifest.json`, or `gui.manifest.json` | `generate` |
| Roslyn transform | `codegen/Novolis.Raylib.CodeGen.Hooks/*.cs` | `generate` |
| New interop template | `RaylibInteropEmitter.cs` + manifest row | `generate` |

```bash
dotnet run --project codegen/Novolis.Raylib.CodeGen -- generate
pwsh ./scripts/agent-verify.ps1
```

Façades emit to **`src/Novolis.Raylib.Runtime/`**. Interop emits to **`src/Novolis.Raylib.Bindings/Interop/`**.

Do not copy generated C# into manifests or hand-patch `*.g.cs`.
